#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:252
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:313
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    @Inject\n"
